These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, software-developer, accountant, writer, bartender, police-officer, freelancer
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, german, colombian, indonesian, polish, dutch, american
 1. the writer is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the polish is the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the right of the police-officer##1
 4. the colombian is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the accountant is in the middle##1
 6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 7. the bartender is the egyptian##1
 8. the architect is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the accountant##1
11. the freelancer is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | bartender | writer | software-developer | accountant | architect | police-officer | freelancer |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | polish   | indonesian      | dutch | colombian    | german    | american         |

