.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: banana, apple, pepper, papaya, lemon, strawberry, apricot
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, r&b, jazz, folk, trance, techno, indie
 1. the fan of trance is the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | banana | apple | lemon | papaya | strawberry | apricot | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | jazz   | folk   | trance      | metal       | indie       | techno     |

