.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, nectarine, garlic, pumpkin, pineapple, broccoli, lime
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, designer, accountant, videographer, nurse, librarian, software-developer
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the software-developer##1
 3. the designer is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the lawyer is the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the accountant is on the right of the designer##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the designer is on the right of the videographer##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the videographer##1
10. the person eating garlic is on the right of the lawyer##1
11. the videographer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | nectarine | pineapple     | garlic  | broccoli       | cherry       | lime  | pumpkin   |
| Job    | librarian  | lawyer | software-developer | videographer | designer | accountant | nurse |

