.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, salsa, ambient, funk, reggae, pop, house
There are 7 different nationalities: mexican, british, american, italian, pakistani, canadian, colombian
 1. the fan of reggae is the british##1
 2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the american##1
 4. the mexican is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 7. the american is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of ambient is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of ambient is the pakistani##1
10. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
11. the colombian is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | house     | funk     | ambient      | salsa | reggae      | d&b     |
| Nationality   | italian | american | canadian | pakistani | colombian | british | mexican |

