.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, photography, puzzles, camping, filmmaking, collecting, skydiving
7 different pets are kept: bird, rat, chinchilla, lizard, hamster, cat, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | photography | puzzles | collecting     | camping | skydiving | filmmaking | chess |
| Pet     | rabbit   | chinchilla    | hamster | cat     | bird         | lizard     | rat        |

