.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, disaster, scientific, epic, sports, thriller, fantasy
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, bus, helicopter, subway, tram, ship, train
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | fantasy | epic | sports | thriller     | disaster | scientific |
| Transport     | ship | subway      | train | helicopter    | tram | bus   | scooter  |

